Description:
You find a large crack in the city wall. The crack is big enough to enter and due to the putrid air coming out of it you are convinced that it is connected to the sewers of the city.

The crack is flooded by the frozen sea water that has probably caused it, luckily the water seems shallow.

To continue you will have to get into the water and cross the crack.
DescriptionAction: It's dark, so you'd better hurry to the other side and get out of the water if you don't want to freeze.
